{"tid":95682,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 － 四喜烤麩","createTime":"2017-01-26T08:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T06:28:26.000Z","uid":30742,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17cba171e1868adb1228c0dfb2ef59ea648615f4","tid":95682,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HYozq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHYozq.jpg&h=a4127c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多年前，老娘在翡翠拉麵小籠包叫過黎食，有d驚艷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時仲未知呢個世界有烤麩呢樣野！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後擺左係個心度，但睇其他人整好似都幾麻煩下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以一直都無動手，直至前排係吉仔記見到有一小塊烤麩賣就心思思想做一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n試過煮完立即食和雪過先係！真係凍左食係好味d！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲可以擺到一排，可以煮多少少放雪櫃！<br />\n得閒拎黎做餸或者送飯，家中兩老又可以食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好唔錯！<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 我覺得呢味野kilo一定好歡喜！但可惜&hellip;&hellip;佢無過黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMy fanspage:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=FK9zgkoCIz6%2BrxlPQjE%2BNHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4a502133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nMy blog:<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=FK9zgkoCIz6%2BrxlPQjE%2BNHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3f286e72\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a><br />\nig: _oldlady_<br />\n四喜烤麩： <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/01/blog-post_25.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F01%2Fblog-post_25.html&d=FK9zgkoCIz6%2BrxlPQjE%2BNHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7f3a9fc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/01/blog-post_25.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca4a68129af10a89c9d6a7879a600fbd8c9546b8","tid":95682,"uid":12879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5966c9fcf8ab0886241622ecc6ea2716c124d019","tid":95682,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869de4fc1213921bb97d796c0a1ba48e5e65017d","tid":95682,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"半個上海人 次撚次過年就見到<br />\n見到都厭"},{"pid":"52bbc1f074502ec451a7b3885c1404a6472f66a5","tid":95682,"uid":5762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"老娘呢排出post密咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打算新年整你嗰個黑啤糖醋骨食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c029f417779932490db8d5d4b6914a0fb0edbba7","tid":95682,"uid":12543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29adca4d5d671